---
/* 搜索触发按钮组件
 * 
 * 2026-03-25: 创建独立触发器，解决 ID 冲突导致的移动端失效问题。
 */
---

<button
  class="search-trigger-btn glass-sm px-3 py-1.5 text-sm flex items-center gap-2 hover:opacity-80 transition-opacity"
  aria-label="搜索文章"
>
  <span>🔍</span>
  <span class="hidden sm:inline">搜索...</span>
  <kbd
    class="hidden sm:inline text-xs px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded"
    style="background: var(--glass-layer-1); color: var(--text-tertiary);"
    >⌘K</kbd
  >
</button>
